Source:  Richmond-Atkinson Papers
Author:
Vol / Page:  1/803
Edition:  1960
Quote:  In the afn. while we [were] sitting on the beach ... a matuku, a small blue heron, came down near us. I have not seen one for several years.
Notes:  (A.S. Atkinson)

